<body>
  <h1>Guess the random number</h1>
  <p>When this page loaded, ruby generated a random number between 1 and 100, you need to enter a number
      between this range and guess the correct number to win the game</p><br>
  <p><%= message %></p>
  <p>You entered: <%= params["guess"] %></p>

  <form action="">
    <label for="guess">Enter a guess:</label>
    <input type="text" name="guess" /><br><br>
    <input type="submit" value="Submit" />
  </form>
  <br>

  <p>You have won: <%= win_count %> time(s)</p>
